26/08/2009
SKOPJE, Macedonia -- A total of 22 police officers have been detained for suspected corruption at the Tabanovce border crossing, police spokesperson Ivo Kotevski said on Tuesday (August 25th). 
He added that an investigation conducted before the arrests spanned seven months. 
(Makfax, MIA, MRT, A1, Greek Foreign Ministry website - 25/08/09)
